(7, '<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n    <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n      <h2>THE FIRST HIGH-COVERAGE COMPLEXION CONCEALER WITH A NATURAL GLOW FINISH</h2>\r\n      <div class=\"row\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-8\">\r\n          <img\r\n            src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-7-description-1.jpg\"\r\n            width=\"85%\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-4 text-center\" style=\"margin:auto; font: 13px, arial;\">\r\n            Composed with 22% pigments, this face and body complexion concealer ensures a high-coverage finish.\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <hr style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n    <div style=\"height: 20px;\"></div>\r\n    <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n        <h2>THE SIGNATURE FRESHNESS OF DIOR HOMME SPORT <br>\r\n          LIKE A BOXER\'S UPPERCUT</h2>\r\n        <hr style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n          <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n            <img width=\"85%\"\r\n              src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-7-description-2.jpg\"\r\n              alt=\"\"><br>\r\n            <span>Imperceptible pearlescent micro-pigments boost radiance to open up the eyes, blur imperfections and brighten the complexion.</span>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n            <img width=\"85%\"\r\n              src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-7-description-3.jpg\"\r\n              alt=\"\"><br>\r\n              <span>Infused with caffeine, it delivers an immediate revitalizing effect to the eye contour area.</span>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n            <img width=\"85%\"\r\n              src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-7-description-4.jpg\"\r\n              alt=\"\"><br>\r\n              <span>Its waterproof, long-wearing and crease-proof formula blends seamlessly with the skin.</span>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n    <hr style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n    <div styl