r\" style=\"margin:auto; font: 1px, arial;\">\r\n              <p>The Dior Homme monolithic bottle is renewed with a lightweight elegance. The clear glass bottle is chiseled with clean, pure lines and topped with the line\'s signature cap, a black cube marked with the DIOR HOMME logo enshrined within a crystalline cube.</p>\r\n              <p>\"It\'s a decidedly new composition, revisited with a notion of carefree elegance. A more sophisticated trail that still retains all of its trademark energy.\" </p>\r\n              <br>\r\n              <p style=\"font-style: italic;\">François Demachy, Dior Perfumer-Creator</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-9 text-center\">\r\n              <img width=\"85%\"\r\n                src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-12-description-4.jpg\"\r\n                alt=\"\">\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"height: 30px;\"></div>\r\n        <div class=\"text-center\" style=\"font: arial;\">\r\n          <h2>\"IF YOU WANT A BOXER, I WILL STEP INTO THE RING FOR YOU.\"</h2>\r\n          <div class=\"image-container\">\r\n            <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n              <video class=\"videoDiv video-mp4\" width=\"85%\" autoplay muted loop>\r\n                <source\r\n                  src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/video/prod-12-description-video-2.mp4\"\r\n                  type=\"video/mp4\">\r\n              </video>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n '),
(13, '<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"text-center\" style=\"font: arial;\">\r\n          <h2>A MANIFESTO OF VIRILITY</h2>\r\n          <div class=\"image-container\">\r\n            <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n              <video class=\"videoDiv video-mp4\" width=\"85%\" autoplay muted loop>\r\n                <source\r\n                  src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/video/prod-13-description-video-1.mp4\"\r\n                  type=\"video/mp4\">\r\n              </video>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <hr style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n        <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n          <h5>THE SIGNATURE FRESHNESS OF DIOR HOMME SPORT <br>\r\n            LIKE A BOXER\'S UPPERCUT</h5>\r\n          <hr style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n          <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n              <img width=\"85%\"\r\n                src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-13-description-1.jpg\"\r\n                alt=\"\"><br>\r\n              <span>Created by François Demachy, Dior Perfumer-Creator </span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n              <img width=\"85%\"\r\n                src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-13-description-2.jpg\"\r\n                alt=\"\"><br>\r\n                <span>Powerful and inviting Rum Absolute is extracted from a Martinican rum</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n              <img width=\"85%\"\r\n                src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-13-description-3.jpg\"\r\n                alt=\"\"><br>\r\n                <span>At a crossroads of spices, Spice Blend intrigues with its powerful and fresh yet fiery signature.</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <hr style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n        <div style=\"height: 10px;\"></div>\r\n        <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n          <h4>A SLEEK NEW BOTTLE</h4>\r\n          <br>\r\n          <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-3 text-center\" style=\"margin:auto; font: 1px, arial;\">\r\n              <p>\"While I don\'t recall the scent of the famous Bay Rhum aftershave, I do remember a bottle in my father\'s medicine cabinet piquing my curiosity. Spice Blend is the olfactory translation of an exotic image that emerges from my childhood. The warm signature of this fragrance is highlighted by a surprising multitude of intertwining spices in dialogue. Like a gust of wind, Spice Blend leaves us wondering if it fans the fire or cools it down.\"</p>\r\n              <br>\r\n              <p style=\"font-style: italic;\">François Demachy, Dior Perfumer-Creator</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-9 text-center\">\r\n              <img width=\"85%\"\r\n                src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-13-description-4.jpg\"\r\n                alt=\"\">\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"height: 30px;\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    '),
