(17, '<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n        <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n          <img\r\n            src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-17-description-1.jpg\"\r\n             width=\"100%\" alt=\"\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"height: 40px;\"></div>\r\n        <hr style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n        <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n          <h1>DISCOVER THE Y COLLECTION</h1>\r\n          <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n              <img width=\"85%\"\r\n                src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-17-description-2.jpg\"\r\n                alt=\"\"><br>\r\n              <b style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\">Y EAU DE PARFUM</b> <br>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n              <img width=\"85%\"\r\n                src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-17-description-3.jpg\"\r\n                alt=\"\"><br>\r\n                <b style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\">Y EAU DE TOILETTE</b> <br>                \r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n              <img width=\"85%\"\r\n                src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-17-description-4.jpg\"\r\n                alt=\"\"><br>\r\n                <b style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\">Y EAU FRAICHE</b> <br>               \r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div style=\"height: 40px;\"></div>\r\n        <hr style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n        <div class=\"text-center\">\r\n          <div class=\"row\">\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n              <img width=\"85%\"\r\n                src=\"/CONCASAU/DOAN/images/prod-17-description-5.jpg\"\r\n                alt=\"\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 text-center\" style=\"font: 13px, arial; margin-top: 100px;\">\r\n              <b style=\"font-size: 1.5rem;\">DARE TO ASK YOURSELF \"WHY NOT?\".</b> <br>\r\n              Daring, determined, cool and charismatic, always pushing back boundaries. And above al